{"tid":1547772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際金融戰線] Fitch Downgrade Hong Kong 惠譽下調香港評級冇人講？","createTime":"2019-09-06T19:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T04:34:27.000Z","uid":265152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e381fe44c4282b07aac529d07d7de12847f2147","tid":1547772,"uid":265152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日見到深藍絲鬧人搞到惠譽下調香港評級(AA+去AA)。評級有幾重要麻煩自己谷歌維基作為一個專業既和理非當然以理為先，詳閱內文。<br />\n<br />\n點知見到(圖內已標示重點)，原來下調評級唔係因為示威者暴力。而係因為示威向國際揭露左香港向中國大陸既制度靠攏，所以評級亦都要靠攏。而因為中國主權評級(A)差過香港(3皮)，所以要下調香港評級。<br />\n<br />\n我謹此多謝深藍絲朋友企出黎怒插中國拖累香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGVwGuD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGVwGuD.jpg&h=70b86f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSeeing an extreme pro-government friend blaming somebodies for triggering a downgrade of Hong Kong's Fitch rating (from AA+ to AA) today, as a professional peaceful-rational-non-violent, I took it deep as reasoning is the priority.<br />\n(Google or Wiki for the importance of ratings)<br />\n<br />\nAfter examination (key points marked in the picture), it turns out that the downgrade was not directly caused by violence of the protestors but it was caused by the intergation of Hong Kong into China's system. Therefore, Hong Kong's rating should converge to China's (A) which is worse (by 3 notches), and hence, should be downgraded.<br />\n<br />\nI now thank my extreme pro-government friend for standing up to criticize China with anger.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNAkzE7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNAkzE7.jpg&h=a5f1ca6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有錯字請見諒"},{"pid":"02fc11b3371bd747ae729b2b87b9e0e51e46cd8d","tid":1547772,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T19:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cWpmiVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"